cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.SI 

This paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence for social good, which falls under the category of cs.AI. The paper also discusses the need for open platforms, which could fall under the category of cs.CY (computers and society) or cs.CR (security and privacy). The examples of social good problems and their AI-based solutions suggest a focus on machine learning and data analysis, which could fall under the categories of cs.LG (machine learning) and cs.SI (social and information networks).
